  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Designing Local Storage**\n\nI\'m currently focused on designing a store, likely a mock service with `localStorage` support. I\'m excited about the possibility of user-submitted quotes from `/oferta` seamlessly adding real entries to `localStorage`, which will then display in both the CRM Kanban and the Clients Table. I will begin by prepopulating the necessary fields.\n\n\n**Populating Initial Data**\n\nI\'ve decided to start populating `/src/initialData.ts` with the realistic lead entries observed, ensuring they perfectly match the screenshot data. I\'ll include the projects for the portfolio, using the provided CDN images. This should provide a good, editable starting point. The file will export `initialLeads` and the `projects` array, making it easily manageable. I am aiming for perfect accuracy with the data from the website!\n\n\n**Adding New Imagery**\n\nI\'ve just added three new images for consideration: an upgrade banner, a CCTV camera facade, and an interior surveillance dome. I am integrating these options as potential assets to enhance the visual appeal and information conveyed by the application.\n\n\n**Incorporating New Visuals**\n\nI\'ve added the new images to the image database. I am now evaluating the best places in the application for their inclusion. Considering the new facade, it will be a perfect addition for a security system banner on the home page. The villa image could work well on the portfolio page.\n\n\n\n**Adding New Images**\n\nI\'ve just added three more images to the database! These include warehouse shelves, premium retail store clothes, and wood chalet doors. I\'m excited about the possibilities they offer for enhancing the visual experience of the application. I plan to integrate these into the existing images.\n\n\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 26
      nanos: 834913183
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
