    thinking: "**Developing Core Views**\n\nI\'ve successfully created the basic structure for Header, Footer, and two core views: Acas\304\203View and ServiciiView. Currently, my focus is on constructing the third core view, PortofoliuView, which should feature hero text introducing portfolio solutions.\n\n\n**Showcasing Client Projects**\n\nI\'m now implementing the first phase of PortofoliuView. I\'ve designed a grid layout for project showcases using a Bento-style asymmetric case.  I\'m populating this with two initial project entries: a residential project featuring a 4K surveillance system and perimeter alarm; and an industrial project highlighting warehouse solutions. I\'m focusing on concise descriptions and relevant imagery.\n\n\n**Expanding Portfolio Showcase**\n\nI\'ve added three new entries to the portfolio: comprehensive protection solutions for large warehouses, anti-theft and customer traffic monitoring for retail showrooms, and security for a tourist guesthouse. I\'m focusing on concise descriptions and impactful imagery. I am implementing this on the grid layout within PortofoliuView.\n\n\n**Refining Portfolio View**\n\nI\'ve just added a new portfolio entry: automated check-in with smart locks and video surveillance for tourist and staff safety. I\'m focusing on user engagement, including a \"Vezi detalii\" modal for each project, which will showcase detailed specs, installed systems, and a comprehensive description. I\'m implementing `/src/components/PortofoliuView.tsx`. Furthermore, I\'ve created a CTA block for the portfolio view.\n\n\n"
